commentTextItems.html: whipped it wide of mid on, ran 3 in the end but only the winning run will count and record the win without breaking a sweat
down the track a step and hits through the line with a wonderfully straight pad giving mid off now chance but to stand and applaud
pushes up to mid on, looking for the run but Sangakkara wasnt interested
on middle and leg and he strokes it though mid wicket with consumate ease
half fwd runs it towards short 3rd standing up as he played it

milestones.description: Ashish Bagai and Joe Harris's 9-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 5 between Mauricette and Tariq Javed

stories.title: Sri Lanka boost NRR with crushing victory
stories.summary: Sri Lanka crushed international minnows Canada with embarrassing ease at Paarl on Wednesday, completing a nine-wicket win inside two hours without the majority of their players even breaking into a sweat
